      <title>特朗普关税承诺导致新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-trails-rest-of-em-as-stimulus-skepticism-sparks-divergence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普加倍强调其征收关税以吸引制造业转移到美国的建议后，新兴市场货币指数收于一个月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-trails-rest-of-em-as-stimulus-skepticism-sparks-divergence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 09:13:52 GMT</pubDate>
